'''Anna''' is a woman in Charlotte's birthing class.

==History==
While the birthing class was doing breathing exercises, Charlotte commented on how ridiculous it was. Anna, who was sitting next to her, scolded her for interrupting. Charlotte explained that when she actually is in labor, she won't care that she paid attention in birthing class.

Later, while entertaining themselves by speculating how each couple conceive, Charlotte said Anna and her husband probably conceived in the missionary position with the lights off and the blinds drawn. Anna said she was ruining the experience for everyone and Charlotte and Cooper were asked to leave.

Anna later walked in on Charlotte and Cooper having sex in the bathroom.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is married.

===Familial===
She and her husband are expecting a baby.
